looking for your child.

84
00:07:19,105 --> 00:07:20,189
[inhales sharply]

85
00:07:20,273 --> 00:07:21,482
[Dr. Lim groans]

86
00:07:21,566 --> 00:07:22,733
[groans]

87
00:07:23,484 --> 00:07:24,777
