91
00:07:38,791 --> 00:07:42,211
The father was a monster.
I'm sure that's left some kind of mark.

92
00:07:43,796 --> 00:07:45,590
That kid can't be normal.

93
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:49,302
[exhales deeply]

94
00:07:49,385 --> 00:07:51,179
