95
00:07:52,889 --> 00:07:54,390
[Dr. Lim sighs deeply]

96
00:07:56,517 --> 00:07:58,019
You don't have time for this.

97
00:07:58,519 --> 00:08:00,771
You gotta find your child before he does.

98
00:08:01,689 --> 00:08:03,941
